### Get repo info
GET {{GITHUB_SERVICE_URL}}/repos/{{GITHUB_OWNER}}/SimpleFaas
Authorization: Bearer {{GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{GITHUB_API_VERSION}}

### Get repo pull requets info
GET {{GITHUB_SERVICE_URL}}/repos/{{GITHUB_OWNER}}/SimpleFaas/pulls
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
Authorization: Bearer {{GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{GITHUB_API_VERSION}}

### List pull request files
GET {{GITHUB_SERVICE_URL}}/repos/{{GITHUB_OWNER}}/SimpleFaas/pulls/1/files
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
Authorization: Bearer {{GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{GITHUB_API_VERSION}}

### List PR comments
GET {{GITHUB_SERVICE_URL}}/repos/{{GITHUB_OWNER}}/SimpleFaas/issues/1/comments
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
Authorization: Bearer {{GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{GITHUB_API_VERSION}}


### Update PR description
PATCH {{GITHUB_SERVICE_URL}}/repos/{{GITHUB_OWNER}}/SimpleFaas/pulls/2
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
Authorization: Bearer {{GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{GITHUB_API_VERSION}}

{"body":"updated body"}

### List reviews for a PR
GET {{GITHUB_SERVICE_URL}}/repos/{{GITHUB_OWNER}}/SimpleFaas/pulls/1/reviews
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
Authorization: Bearer {{GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{GITHUB_API_VERSION}}

### List issue (PR) comments
GET {{GITHUB_SERVICE_URL}}/repos/{{GITHUB_OWNER}}/SimpleFaas/issues/2/comments
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
Authorization: Bearer {{GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{GITHUB_API_VERSION}}

### Create an issue (PR) comment
POST {{GITHUB_SERVICE_URL}}/repos/{{GITHUB_OWNER}}/SimpleFaas/issues/2/comments
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
Authorization: Bearer {{GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{GITHUB_API_VERSION}}

{
  "body": "Hello GitHub commenting world!"
}
